{"tid":1532251,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"而家謝重警告你地，邊撚過再Fact check一D唔會有實際答案既野，小心我直接當你係左膠共諜","createTime":"2019-09-02T13:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:45:46.000Z","uid":187700,"like":14,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd7be3ea12cd4e60eda222552a6ede150b35fe0","tid":1532251,"uid":187700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:04:21.000Z","msg":"好簡單，呢一刻對家會有幾過份，基本上已經唔需要再質疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為由612開始，幾乎每一日都有人去要求Fact Check一D唔會有答案既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然，邊度有刀手，邊度有狗會點包圍既，個D要Check係必須，因為要預防<br />\n而且會可以影到有相有片，所以呢D唔會有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但呢期新屋嶺同太子個D要Check驚炒車既，我只會講：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母啦呢D野Check撚到啊！？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有相有片有名單有死亡證既，個D先叫Check撚到啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定你想要唔會有可能承受到二次傷害既女事主驗到精液DNA?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾魔警NTR既，班魔警無可能會低能到唔戴套，事後一定用水喉灌陰道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你想點Check啊？定想係PornHub見到有片先信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講太子，真係死Q左既，醫護無可能放到死亡證出黎，更無可能幫你影條屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家係個撚個係度尻講炒車，到呢一刻實際數字都未核對到啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有對家唔屌，屌自己人放Fake News做乜撚野？<br />\n你不如去埋對面新聞部做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦，魔警同黨鐵根本有片都唔會拎出黎<br />\n真係NTR左打死左人，都唔會承認！<br />\n你班冷氣軍師係度不停去撲滅同路人把火<br />\n咁你幫對家助攻唔係共諜係乜撚野？<br />\n同尋日東涌阻手足教訓拎磚打手足後頸既左膠有乜分別！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而家擺明係唔撚岩聽架啦！</strong></span><br />\n但有D野擺明No sence既，唔該唔好去做搞到變相拖後腿<br />\n咁叻既你一係下次開始落場去班魔警面前講愛與和平！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49676e2418a8ee54fe59618f622131184888f315","tid":1532251,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7182e923e86fa818d3dadee3cc00e5bc6778d009","tid":1532251,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"65add220e63520cb7fcec18c9ce63b5a77b39dac","tid":1532251,"uid":31646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"我個睇法都係咁 但好似好多人都唔buy咁"},{"pid":"b41bef6c59ddb19f59e9126d36bcfd2dfd4005b6","tid":1532251,"uid":187700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:21:00.000Z","msg":"留底3豪子俾班共諜啊<br />\n政戰唔識做日日拖後腿<br />\n你對得住死左既人？"},{"pid":"2d235f81b2fbb7806c62ee556d5dd43e9ff10afa","tid":1532251,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"唔check未比人干擾哂真消息囉，整整吓黑警就可以不停放假消息拉人不停放假消息令真正義士消息見唔到光"},{"pid":"3c9d286e2145e133c1a71b8390239ced254a3a24","tid":1532251,"uid":223727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"太陽由東邊升起<br />\n聽日日出時間六點<br />\n已fact check"},{"pid":"9995e06920f0d7580c1800de498d43330db35fe5","tid":1532251,"uid":229225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"根本對家就成日用 D 證實唔到既陰謀論黎攻擊我地<br />\n要反駁呢 D 陰謀論亦極其困難"},{"pid":"e3acad01c0b1f40c9d9680499640d317dfa470d4","tid":1532251,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shockin