com/thread/1529606/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1529606/page/1</a><br />\n簡單D講， 所有Secret page都係google form投稿<br />\n唔洗講明咩所屬，姐係外人都可以入去交form作故仔<br />\n再睇返當日HA Secret個post已經del左<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/731331330322257/posts/2321502444638463?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F731331330322257%2Fposts%2F2321502444638463%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1agNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=10628b8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/731331330322257/posts/2321502444638463?sfns=mo</a><br />\n已fact check？你Fact check左D咩啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有啊，醫院聯網check唔到跨區，殮房資料唔係個個人開到黎睇架！<br />\n咁而家又係無明確答案，點解有人又會可以大聲宣傳係Fake news?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三單最新鮮既：有段疑似手足出文認831凌晨落刀<br />\n突發！8月30日晚斬狗事件有手足認咗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533690</a><br />\n內文如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/19uVZkLMrMdpr8ZIeBjkc236oR2U2S3fGZ4QPa5_nmZA/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F19uVZkLMrMdpr8ZIeBjkc236oR2U2S3fGZ4QPa5_nmZA%2Fedit&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1agNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=b51e7819\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/19uVZkLMrMdpr8ZIeBjkc236oR2U2S3fGZ4QPa5_nmZA/edit</a><br />\n即係咁，隔住個mon你講你係李嘉誠我都唔會有得check<br />\n就咁一份你我都寫到出黎既文<br />\n證明到出文者就係本人？<br />\n當日斬人者有無五官圖出過for通輯？無<br />\n出文者有無出自己樣同當日落刀圖片？無<br />\n係乜證據都無既時候，又點fact check出文者係刀手呢？<br />\n(先講明，個人判斷份野係流既)<br />\n<br />\n首先我無否認Fact Check既重要性<br />\n但Fact Check唔係口講就當係<br />\n要真係有圖有片先佐證到<br />\n證明唔到既野就只係<span style=\"color: red;\">Fact Check唔到</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而唔係Fake News</span></strong><br />\n明未？"},{"pid":"52d4f533630b2bb486f44c39dae36ee060972ff9","tid":1532251,"uid":187700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi